Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:01:54.32,Main,Murakami,0,0,0,,เห็นไหม !
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:54.97,Main,Murakami,0,0,0,,ดูสิ !
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.97,0:01:55.69,Main,Murakami,0,0,0,,ดูสิ !
